00:01:58,456 --> 00:02:02,000
Scarlet Heart
Episode 24

24
00:02:23,239 --> 00:02:26,180
This snuff bottle, do you still want it?

25
00:02:30,282 --> 00:02:32,100
If you have the nerve, then keep it.

26
00:02:33,193 --> 00:02:35,422
Just do not regret it in the future.

27
00:02:37,620 --> 00:02:40,180
Give it to her.  I am afraid that the item was from someone powerful.

28
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:41,580
Quick, just return it to her.

29
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:47,300
I gave it back.

30
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,900
Today, an event happening like this.

31
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:58,480
It is not what I wished for.

32
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:02,120
Since, we still have to spend a long time together in the future,

33
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,460
I want to let you know something clearly.

34
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:08,220
As they say,

35
00:03:08,220 --> 00:03:10,600
a phoenix without tail feathers is worse off than a chicken.

36
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:12,340
But it is also said that a centipede with a thousand legs

37
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:14,100
dies but never falls down.

38
00:03:14,740 --> 00:03:16,560
You have been in the palace for many years.

39
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:18,180
Promotions and demotions,

40
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:19,820
you should have seen plenty.

41
00:03:19,820 --> 00:03:23,180
You should leave a space for yourselves in everything.

42
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:26,380
I know,

43
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:28,460
Eunuch Zhang normally gives me special treatment

44
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:31,220
and you all have suffered a lot.

45
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:34,700
That is my wrong.

46
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,400
From today on,

47
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,460
we should all understand each other more,

48
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:44,260
try to make less mistakes,

49
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:47,580
so events like this will not happen again.

50
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:49,620
If there are more events like this...

51
00:03:49,620 --> 00:03:53,820
I am going to ask everyone to please excuse me now,

52
00:03:57,060 --> 00:03:59,140
but those who treat me badly,

53
00:03:59,140 --> 00:04:01,800
I won't quickly forget.

54
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,660
Any person who treats me well,

55
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:07,020
I will definitely remember and repay their kindness.

56
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:10,460
In truth, I had already planned to give gifts to my sisters.

57
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:13,060
I just did not know your preferences in this short a time,

58
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:15,140
so I did not casually give out gifts.

59
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:26,660
Mei'mei (Younger Sister).  Please accept this for my sake.

60
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:31,220
If you don't mind, then I will take one too.

61
00:04:31,220 --> 00:04:33,000
Sure.

62
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:35,340
We are all sisters.  Please don't be too polite.

63
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:37,140
Thank you.

64
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,140
Alright, alright.

65
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:40,420
Eat some melon seeds.  Eat some melon seeds.

66
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:42,820
Today's seeds are extra tasty. Delicious and crunchy.

67
00:04:42,820 --> 00:04:45,180
Come, come, come. Let's eat together

68
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:51,740
Eat. Eat.

69
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:54,340
Greetings, Lady Rouxi.

70
00:05:55,180 --> 00:05:56,100
Eunuch Cao.

71
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:58,740
Please do not be like that.  I do not deserve it.

72
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:02,960
Getting to see Lady was not an easy task.

73
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:05,020
Wang'ye (Prince} sent this to you.

74
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,660
Inside there are banknotes of small amounts.

75
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:10,980
Keep those with you so you don't need to worry about losing things that are not easy to give away.

76
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:14,060
The medicine you wanted was sent to your room already.

77
00:06:14,780 --> 00:06:16,060
Thank you very much,  Eunuch Cao.

78
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:18,780
If you have anything you need, you can come find me.

79
00:06:18,780 --> 00:06:20,900
I will take my leave now.

80
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:29,620
Eunuch Zhang.

81
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:31,540
Can you...

82
00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:33,740
No need for that, no need.

83
00:06:33,740 --> 00:06:36,340
Then I will take my leave.

84
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,940
Rouxi.

85
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:48,580
Eunuch Zhang.

86
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:50,300
Follow me.

87
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:52,860
Yes.

88
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:16,140
10th Prince. 14th Prince.

89
00:07:19,060 --> 00:07:21,820
Greetings to the Princes.

90
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,240
What are you doing here?

91
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,780
Why are you like this?

92
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:26,640
Didn't you say everything had been arranged well?

93
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:28,940
A certain work must have a certain look.

94
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:30,980
How is Zhang'xian'yin (treacherous) treating you?

95
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:33,260
Eunuch Zhang has been taking good care of me.

96
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:36,220
If he dares to treat you in any beastly manner, I will have his head fall to the ground!

97
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:37,820
I know.

98
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:41,940
Alright, let's sit and talk.

99
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:43,420
Is there anything wrong?

100
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,300
Is it my sister?

101
00:07:47,780 --> 00:07:49,400
Your sister is well,

102
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:51,020
even though her body is weak.

103
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:52,420
But you already knew

104
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:54,900
because she's always been like this throughout the years.

105
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:58,100
Then what's wrong

106
00:07:58,100 --> 00:08:00,460
that both Princes personally looked for me?

107
00:08:00,460 --> 00:08:02,180
After the dead eagle event,

108
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:03,900
8th Prince suffered a big shock

109
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:05,420
and was very sick.

110
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:07,220
Though his illness has gone,

111
00:08:07,220 --> 00:08:09,520
he is still feeling very discouraged,

112
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:12,780
8th Brother has not been very healthy.  So with the pressure from inside and outside,

113
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:14,580
he has become sick again.

114
00:08:14,580 --> 00:08:17,320
This time the illness is more serious.

115
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,220
The Imperial Physician said...

116
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:22,700
Imperial father spoke four words to the Imperial Physician,

117
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:24,380
"Use your best treatments."

118
00:08:26,620 --> 00:08:29,880
Ruoxi, that's why we came to look for you.

119
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:32,560
If you have anything to tell him,

120
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:34,740
tell us and we will pass it on.

121
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:36,420
A letter is alright too.

122
00:08:36,420 --> 00:08:38,740
Did 8th Prince send you two here?

123
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:40,700
It was my idea.

124
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:42,819
8th prince has been unconscious.

125
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:47,900
Rouxi, what happened between you and 8th Brother?

126
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:49,860
How is everything in the 8th Prince's manor?

127
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:51,980
How are 8th Fu'jin and my sister?
( Fu'jin - Legal wife, sister is 2nd wife/concubine)

128
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:54,020
8th Sister-in-law is really a hero among women,

129
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:56,100
I admire her wholeheartedly.

130
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:59,100
Think about it.  After 13th Brother got into trouble

131
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:01,220
and his manor became a total mess,

132
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:03,700
even such things as petty thefts happened.

133
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:05,020
13th Fu'jin

134
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:08,620
had to dismiss all her unnecessary servants.

135
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:09,720
However, 8th Sister-in-law

136
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:13,100
did not allow any trouble to happen in his manor.

137
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,220
About your sister,

138
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,820
on behalf of you and 8th Prince,

139
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:21,780
she worries day and night. She kneels in front of Buddha chanting and praying.

140
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:23,740
I heard from Qiao'hui
(Qiao 'house' maid)

141
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:26,180
she will cry several times a day.

142
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:31,460
Please wait then.

143
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:38,580
[ Happiness causes worry and suffering.]

144
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:41,140
[ Happiness causes fear and fright. ]

145
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:43,520
[ There will be no worry and suffering without happiness. ]

146
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:45,980
[ Fear and fright should be nowhere to find. ]

147
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,720
[ Love creates worry and suffering to grow. ]

148
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:51,520
[ Love also creates more fear and fright. ]

149
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,240
[ Without love there will be no worries and suffering, ]

150
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,760
[ Fear and fright will be nowhere to be found. ]

151
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:00,800
[ Therefore, one should not love ]

152
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:03,720
[ because love and separation create suffering. ]

153
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:06,040
[ If there is no love or hate ]

154
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:09,400
[ you will be free without any burdens. ]

155
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:16,400
The ability of Beile'ye is enough to fix the whole realm.

156
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:20,200
The love of Beile'ye is like flowers in a mirror and the moon reflected in water.

157
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,880
Beile'ye, you have high ambitions.

158
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:26,040
Even though you put all your heart into the empire,

159
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:29,320
you are not someone who does not have emotion.

160
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,700
"If there is no love or hate,

161
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:35,000
you will be free without burdens."

162
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,000
In this letter from Ruoxi to me,

163
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,660
she advises me that

164
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:43,960
one should guard their self against worry and fear.

165
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:50,140
I think she found a way to have a peace of mind in that laundry place.

166
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:53,985
So Beile'ye, you should not worry anymore.

167
00:10:55,796 --> 00:10:58,118
You can even imitate her.

168
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,764
I never thought that

169
00:11:02,089 --> 00:11:04,411
she would have such a strong will.

170
00:11:06,106 --> 00:11:08,776
I am defeated.

171
00:11:09,264 --> 00:11:11,307
She is not.

172
00:11:12,468 --> 00:11:14,233
Previously,

173
00:11:14,233 --> 00:11:17,344
I worried about her every day.

174
00:11:18,668 --> 00:11:20,880
I don't know when it started

175
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,964
but that most troublesome girl

176
00:11:23,242 --> 00:11:25,720
suddenly grew up.

177
00:11:26,818 --> 00:11:28,583
Now the roles are reversed.

178
00:11:29,047 --> 00:11:32,066
We have to learn from her not to give up.

179
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,328
She has taught me

180
00:11:37,708 --> 00:11:40,200
what it really means to let everything go.

181
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:42,143
Before, because of love, I

182
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:45,301
could not break my self away from hate.

183
00:11:47,530 --> 00:11:49,759
But Ruo'xi says,

184
00:11:51,408 --> 00:11:53,519
once everything is released,

185
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:55,160
there will be no more pain or suffering.

186
00:11:57,956 --> 00:12:00,471
Once, I hated you, Beile'ye,

187
00:12:00,471 --> 00:12:02,440
but after I read this letter,

188
00:12:03,366 --> 00:12:04,840
I know

189
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:08,150
that the person who is making me unhappy was not someone else,

190
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:09,821
it was me, myself.

191
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,320
A proverb says,

192
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,840
'Life hurriedly counts ten years'.

193
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:20,100
Why should I burden myself with something that I could take with me

194
00:12:20,108 --> 00:12:22,280
that would suffocate me.

195
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:31,440
[ 56th year of Kangxi's reign, the Empress Dowager passes away ]

196
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:40,007
I just received an urgent message.

197
00:12:40,007 --> 00:12:42,362
Sele and Eluntejun

198
00:12:42,362 --> 00:12:44,698
were finally heavily surrounded when they marched in.

199
00:12:44,698 --> 00:12:47,020
Their whole army was completely annihilated.

200
00:12:48,390 --> 00:12:50,100
Do you two have any opinions?

201
00:12:50,100 --> 00:12:51,362
Replying to Your Majesty,

202
00:12:51,362 --> 00:12:52,680
your servant thinks this way.

203
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:54,657
Since Zun'ge'er just won recently, I think

204
00:12:54,657 --> 00:12:56,460
so their morale was very high.

205
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:58,680
Our army should avoid their vanguard

206
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,534
and ask for an armistice.

207
00:13:00,534 --> 00:13:02,616
When should this armistice end?

208
00:13:02,616 --> 00:13:06,360
That... That needs to be carefully considered for the long-term results.

209
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,340
Replying to Your Majesty,

210
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:09,280
I also agree with an armistice for now.

211
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:11,880
The roads to Tibet are often rugged and dangerous.

212
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:14,640
Impediments to transportation become a problem.

213
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:17,300
What if ambushes cause rations and animal fodder to become insufficient,

214
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:20,431
what would happen to our army?

215
00:13:20,431 --> 00:13:21,960
Was this your first time knowing

216
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,680
how to fight over there?

217
00:13:24,195 --> 00:13:27,180
Are you now so scared to death by the enemy army

218
00:13:27,180 --> 00:13:29,080
you're unwilling to fight?

219
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,220
To protect the realm,

220
00:13:31,220 --> 00:13:33,901
ten thousand deaths will not prevent me!

221
00:14:03,506 --> 00:14:04,800
Your Majesty,

222
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:07,200
you did not sleep for several nights,

223
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:09,800
please take care of your health.

224
00:14:11,912 --> 00:14:14,800
All of the northwest area belongs to

225
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:17,160
King Cealabudan now,

226
00:14:18,831 --> 00:14:21,618
how can I sleep well?

227
00:14:23,919 --> 00:14:26,760
I underestimated the enemy.

228
00:14:34,894 --> 00:14:36,880
[ The northwest area was occupied ]

229
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:39,440
[ but the military officials in the Imperial Court did not support the Emperor sending in army reinforcements. ]

230
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:42,180
[ Due to the urgent situation both outside and inside, ]

231
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:47,080
[ the Emperor moved the date up and appointed the 14th Prince as the Fuyuan General. ]

232
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,800
[ He took command and lead the (replacement) army to the frontier. ]

233
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:19,018
Move out!

234
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:28,820
14th Brother is very clever.

235
00:16:28,820 --> 00:16:30,080
He is capable and has a refined character.

236
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:32,760
We, brothers, cannot compare to him.

237
00:16:38,340 --> 00:16:40,160
9th Brother.

238
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:42,920
8th brother. The wind here is strong.

239
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:44,840
You just recovered from illness and should not stand out here a long time.

240
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:46,560
I should accompany you back inside.

241
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:48,380
Compared to 14th Brother,

242
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:50,280
standing a while is just a small matter.

243
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,920
As long as the General

244
00:16:52,920 --> 00:16:55,140
can save the common people from a predicament

245
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:57,080
and not disappoint Imperial Father,

246
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:59,049
my wishes will be fulfilled.

247
00:17:00,373 --> 00:17:03,500
The Emperor gave 14th Prince such an important duty.

248
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:06,160
It seems that he will become the Crown Prince.

249
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:10,040
That's right. The Emperor even said 14th Prince is the most similar to himself.

250
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,980
Among all the Princes,

251
00:17:11,980 --> 00:17:15,319
the 14th prince has become the first one among the brothers.

252
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:16,820
No one else can touch him.

253
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:18,345
Yes.

254
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:45,640
Master.  The 4th Prince is asking to see the Emperor.

255
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,378
- Leave.
- Yes.

256
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:49,600
Emperor.

257
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:51,975
4th Prince is outside and is asking to see you.

258
00:17:52,375 --> 00:17:52,890
Let him in.

259
00:17:52,890 --> 00:17:53,960
