I eat but do not know the taste of what I eat.

531
00:32:29,340 --> 00:32:32,819
Whatever your body lacks is what you need the most.

532
00:32:32,819 --> 00:32:36,960
Emperor, please pick some foods and give up some foods based on whatever food you want.

