534
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:42,280
Pastry.

535
00:32:46,997 --> 00:32:50,360
It's been so long since I've eaten any pastries.

536
00:32:52,224 --> 00:32:55,357
It has been a very long time.

537
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:12,580
Eunuch Wang.

538
00:33:12,580 --> 00:33:15,140
Elder Sister, you made me wait so long!

539
00:33:15,140 --> 00:33:16,905
Elder Sister, come with me, please get into the palanquin.

540
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:39,428
Eunuch Wang.

