His Majesty wants to eat some delicious things.

544
00:33:46,766 --> 00:33:48,440
The imperial kitchen has exhausted all their ideas.

545
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:49,884
The imperial kitchen wanted to come up with a plan but just couldn't.

546
00:33:49,884 --> 00:33:51,240
My Master guessed

547
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:52,460
His Majesty was thinking of you

548
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:54,940
