551
00:33:57,340 --> 00:33:59,840
Since he couldn't wait, he asked for you to come to the Palace instead.

552
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:02,671
Is His Majesty's body all right?

553
00:34:02,671 --> 00:34:06,247
Much better, just easily irritated.

554
00:34:09,337 --> 00:34:11,230
If I did not remember wrong

555
00:34:11,230 --> 00:34:13,724
