556
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:17,680
November of Kangxi year 61.

557
00:34:18,220 --> 00:34:20,713
Everything will not be far off.

558
00:34:42,359 --> 00:34:44,079
I'll leave now.

559
00:34:46,998 --> 00:34:49,160
Sister, you have returned.

560
00:34:53,720 --> 00:34:57,840
Must have been hard for you all these years.

561
00:35:14,516 --> 00:35:17,800
Sister, do you want to go to my rooms to rest a bit?

562
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,000
No need.

563
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:22,492
Bringing me directly to the kitchens will be fine.

564
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:27,960
This should be the last time I'll get to make pastries for His Majesty.

565
00:35:28,540 --> 00:35:31,300
In regards to His Majesty,

566
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:33,960
I have fears and

567
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:37,516
I have compassion.

568
00:35:38,060 --> 00:35:40,480
All that has now changed into not willing to be apart.

569
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:43,251
I am just waiting for that moment to come.

570
00:36:26,200 --> 00:36:29,227
This was not made by Yutan.

571
00:36:30,980 --> 00:36:33,429
Tell her to come see me.

572
00:36:43,260 --> 00:36:45,200
One taste, I

573
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:46,920
knew that this pastry

574
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:48,864
was made by you.

575
00:36:48,864 --> 00:36:51,960
This light and non-greasy pastry

576
00:36:53,050 --> 00:36:55,000
has really

577
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:58,100
whetted my usually poor appetite.

578
00:36:58,100 --> 00:37:01,760
I am willing to make pastries for you anytime

579
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:04,840
if it can help to benefit your health.

580
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:06,440
Good.

581
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:11,720
Raise your head now.

582
00:37:12,700 --> 00:37:15,320
Let me see you properly.

583
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,940
Your face is so pale!

584
00:37:23,780 --> 00:37:25,680
Have you been sick?

585
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:29,360
Replying to His Majesty, I have been well.

586
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:31,860
Then why is your complexion not so good?

587
00:37:31,860 --> 00:37:33,160
Replying to Your Majesty,

588
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:35,680
I've only had some small aches.

589
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,420
That is nothing worthy of mentioning.

590
00:37:37,618 --> 00:37:39,400
No need for Your Majesty to worry.

591
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:43,809
One's body, skin, and hair are all gifts from one's parents.

592
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:49,080
You must take better care of your health.

593
00:37:49,080 --> 00:37:52,000
I will listen to the Emperor's words

594
00:37:58,120 --> 00:38:01,520
His Majesty did not say if I could come home?

595
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:03,760
Letting you stay was actually Eunuch Li's suggestion.

596
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:05,620
But the bigger part of it was His Majesty's idea.

597
00:38:05,620 --> 00:38:08,004
Jie'jie. Don't worry about that

598
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:13,800
Yutan, has the Emperor mentioned anything about you leaving the palace?

599
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:18,040
His Majesty doesn't know how old I am.

600
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:20,080
The empire has been at war.

601
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:21,480
The State Treasury has a tight budget

602
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:22,920
and various disasters are continually happening.

603
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,720
The Emperor's heart is completely focused on that.

604
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:25,900
For us lowly people,

605
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:27,560
he does not have the energy left to be considerate.

606
00:38:27,660 --> 00:38:28,740
Then how can Eunuch Li

607
00:38:28,740 --> 00:38:30,899
not worry?

608
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:33,080
He also asked me twice for my opinion.

609
00:38:33,080 --> 00:38:34,680
I didn't want to go outside the palace.

610
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:36,400
So he didn't bring it up again.

611
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:37,640
Anyway,

612
00:38:37,640 --> 00:38:39,407
Eunuch Li would love for me to stay.

613
00:38:39,407 --> 00:38:43,926
Whenever Eunuch Li wants something to do done, he will ask me or Eunuch Wang to handle it.

614
00:38:44,040 --> 00:38:48,360
In order to train a proper servant, changing over every three to five years is not doable.

615
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:50,320
That is true.

616
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:52,800
This time the Emperor's sickness

617
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:54,780
is very severe.

618
00:38:54,780 --> 00:38:58,066
I don't think that the Emperor's illness is quite that severe.

619
00:38:58,066 --> 00:38:59,180
But this time, with Sister coming back

620
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:01,880
the Emperor took pity on you.

621
00:39:02,080 --> 00:39:05,543
Maybe he'll let you continue serving him,

622
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:08,280
but your complexion does not look too good either.

623
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:12,720
If Jie'jie really could come back here, I will need to nurse Jie'jie back to being more healthy.

624
00:39:14,701 --> 00:39:16,480
Even the close servants

625
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:19,240
do not think his sickness is too serious.

626
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:21,280
Therefore the officials in the Imperial Court

627
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:23,028
will also treat it lightly.

628
00:39:23,228 --> 00:39:24,440
I don't remember if the Emperor

629
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:27,120
died of the current illness.

630
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:32,320
In the days that came later, people were suspicious of why Kang'xi would die all of a sudden.

631
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:36,360
It can't be...

632
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:39,514
Sister, what's wrong?

633
00:39:40,723 --> 00:39:44,321
These last few days, did 4th prince come here a lot?

634
00:39:44,680 --> 00:39:46,280
He came daily.

635
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:48,380
Sometimes even 3 or 4 times.

636
00:39:48,380 --> 00:39:50,360
Even when the Emperor was in bad spirits

637
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:51,680
and stopped seeing the Princes.

638
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:54,480
But he would still see the Fourth Prince.

639
00:39:55,754 --> 00:39:59,019
Why do you ask?

640
00:39:59,230 --> 00:40:02,800
Which prince do you think Emperor will pick?

641
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:06,200
It should be 14th Prince.

642
00:40:06,440 --> 00:40:07,660
His Majesty has been pondering

643
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:10,360
if he should call 14th Prince to return,

644
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,858
but he was almost home anyway.

645
00:40:12,858 --> 00:40:15,880
But isn't the Emperor good to the 4th prince too?

646
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:18,400
Yes, among the brothers,

647
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:21,560
the ones he dotes on the most are the 14th and the 4th.

648
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,460
Sister,

649
00:40:23,460 --> 00:40:24,820
don't think too much.

650
00:40:24,820 --> 00:40:27,040
I will get you some warm water.

651
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:33,280
Did 4th Prince do something?

652
00:40:35,020 --> 00:40:39,360
No.  He wouldn't.

653
00:40:39,386 --> 00:40:40,420
Imperial Father.

654
00:40:40,420 --> 00:40:41,680
You didn't sleep well again.

655
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:43,600
Did the coughing interrupt your sleep?

656
00:40:43,600 --> 00:40:44,640
I never thought

657
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:47,580
the cold would come on so strongly and quickly.

658
00:40:47,580 --> 00:40:49,276
The Imperial Physicians said that

659
00:40:49,276 --> 00:40:50,640
as long as you take care

660
00:40:50,640 --> 00:40:51,616
and eat the medicine on time,

661
00:40:51,616 --> 00:40:54,100
you will get better naturally.

662
00:40:54,100 --> 00:40:55,480
Here.

663
00:41:13,782 --> 00:41:15,621
Rouxi.

664
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:18,160
Have you seen the doctor yet?

665
00:41:18,160 --> 00:41:19,960
Not yet.

666
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:22,360
You forgot!

667
00:41:22,522 --> 00:41:24,840
Thank you, for your concern.

668
00:41:28,980 --> 00:41:33,760
4th Son, sit with me a while.

669
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:35,880
Thank you, Imperial Father.

670
00:41:41,340 --> 00:41:43,800
Recently, the empire's matters are extremely tight

671
00:41:44,060 --> 00:41:46,520
and the war is still ongoing.

672
00:41:46,520 --> 00:41:49,360
My health has become worse.

673
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:51,880
I really feel that the spirit is willing but the flesh is weak.

674
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:53,480
Imperial Father, your body is under the influence of cold,

675
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:56,160
