676
00:41:56,160 --> 00:41:57,840
That is why you would have such thoughts.

677
00:41:59,100 --> 00:42:01,160
I am getting old,

678
00:42:01,815 --> 00:42:03,280
many things,

679
00:42:03,387 --> 00:42:06,880
