691
00:43:04,920 --> 00:43:06,450
Your Highness.

692
00:43:08,347 --> 00:43:10,200
Is there anything wrong?

693
00:43:10,530 --> 00:43:12,740
Imperial Father ordered Prince to host the Sacrifice to the Heavens ceremony.

694
00:43:12,740 --> 00:43:15,760
